        参数:
        

        eventCode - install/uninstall result
     public static final int EVENT_INSTALL_SUCCESS = 0;           //安装成功
     public static final int EVENT_INSTALL_FAIL_PACKAGE_ERROR = 1;//安装包有问题
     public static final int EVENT_INSTALL_FAIL_VERSION_LOW = 2;  //安装版本低于当前版本
     public static final int EVENT_INSTALL_FAIL_PATH_ERROR = 3;   //安装包路径有问题
     public static final int EVENT_UNINSTALL_SUCCESS = 10;        //卸载成功
     public static final int EVENT_UNINSTALL_FAIL_OTHER = 12;     //卸载的其他问题
